Task: Fix GraalVM 'unexpected interop primitive' test failures

## Summary
Resolved 39 failing tests (330 total) caused by GraalVM JS engine
cross-ScriptContext object migration errors.

## Root Cause
chai/Ajv JS objects were loaded into the engine's default ScriptContext
during initialization, then stored as Java references (chaiRef/ajvRef)
and injected into isolated Bindings ScriptContexts per-execution.
GraalVM's OtherContextGuestObject.migrateReturn() asserted failure when
migrating JS objects across context boundaries, producing:
  'unexpected interop primitive' AssertionError (PolyglotException)

## Changes in ScriptExecutionService.kt

### Binding injection strategy (critical fix)
- REMOVED: engine.createBindings() + engine.eval(script, bindings)
- ADDED: engine.getBindings(ENGINE_SCOPE) + engine.eval(script)
  pm/am Java objects now injected directly into the global ENGINE_SCOPE
  so scripts can access chai/Ajv from the global JS scope without
  any cross-context migration.

### JS object reference elimination
- REMOVED: chaiRef: Any? and ajvRef: Any? fields (held GraalVM JS Values)
- ADDED: hasChaiLoaded: Boolean and hasAjvLoaded: Boolean flags
  Only boolean presence flags retained; no GraalVM JS object references.

### JS preamble test() wrapper
- CHANGED: test: function(n, f) { __jpm.test(n, f) }
  → test: function(n, f) { executes f() in JS; calls __jpm.recordTest(n, passed, err) }
  JS functions no longer cross the host/guest boundary — only String/Boolean primitives do.

### New Java API
- ADDED: TestContext.recordTest(name: String, passed: Boolean, error: String)
- ADDED: PmBinding.recordTest(...) delegate
- RESTORED: TestContext.test(name: String, fn: () -> Boolean) to canonical Kotlin signature
- ADDED: ScriptExecutionService two-arg constructor for test compatibility

### chai Proxy fix
- ADDED: engine.eval('chai.config.useProxy = false') immediately after loading chai
  Disables ES6 Proxy-based assertion chains globally; avoids Reflect.get()
  incompatibility in GraalVM fallback runtime (no JVMCI/JIT).

## Files Modified
- src/main/kotlin/com/github/dhzhu/amateurpostman/services/ScriptExecutionService.kt

